                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d137">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">824.24/869: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Bolivia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Boal</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-09-21">September 21,
                            1943</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1172. The Department’s 1168, September 20, 6 p.m. The Department and OEW are
                    reluctant to announce the amendment to Plan A without Bolivia’s participation,
                    but announcement cannot be delayed <pb facs="0157" n="145" xml:id="pg_145"/>
                    beyond Thursday morning.<note n="49" xml:id="d137fn49">September 23.</note>
                    Please telephone by Wednesday afternoon at the latest.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
